entries.title_d: Try to find a ship of the Imperial Inquisition that is relatively alone. We will provide you with coordinates to search.
entries.title: Dathomir system: Patrol for lone Imperial ships.
entries.split_quest_alert: Brother Ezkiel: < Blast it! Our systems are warning us that there are more enemies in the area. Keep a lookout and try to single out a target. We need it disabled, information is important to us at this stage. >
entries.quest_patrol_d: We are updating your ship with new coordinates as you search for small groups of Imperial ships.
entries.quest_location_d: The Dathomir system is dangerous and the area you will patrol in is no exception as it's close to Imperial Navy fleets.
